data.title: Enterprise Utah Zip Code List
data.meta_description: A list of all the zip codes and maps associated with Enterprise, UT - Washington County Utah City of Enterprise zip code map
data.text: Enterprise, UT is a city located in Washington County, Utah and has a land area of 150.41 square miles (389.56 km2). The water area for the city is 0.68 square miles or 1.76 km2. There is one unique zip code in Enterprise, Utah and it is 84725. The area code(s) for Enterprise is 435.
